  <brief_title>Cardiac Functions in Living Donor Liver Transplant Recipients. An Echocardiographic Study.</brief_title>
  <official_title>Cardiac Functions in Living Donor Liver Transplant Recipients. An Echocardiographic Study.</official_title>
